                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">No Doubt the Best E2k3 book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>9</span>
